MMARIAN (Linguistic Tagging)**\nEach word was assigned one of the seven strict Part of Speech categories: Noun, Verb, Adjective, Adverb, Pronoun, Preposition, Conjunction. No sub-details or tenses were included.\n\n**PROTOCOL 7: THE FILTER (Size Constraint)**\nAll words and roots included in the final dataset consist of at least two characters, adhering to the size constraint.\n\n**Scholarly Guesses:**\nFor proper nouns like 'አማርቲያ' and 'ቶሩ', the assumption was made that they are indeed proper names, given their common transliterations in other languages (e.g., Amartya Sen, Toru). The 'importance' field was uniformly set to 7 as no specific criteria for differential importance were provided.","input_words":["በመልቀቅም","በነጃት","ያለበርትን","አማርቲያ","ሴንን","ለክቡርነትዎ","የተኙበትንም","ከመግጠሙ","ሳያፈስና","የቆች","ተገላይ","ተገላይነት","መነበይቲና","እንሸልላለን","ታነቢው","ጨቀጨቅከን","አሸማቀቀው","የቶሩና","በመሄት","እሚያሠራን","እሚያደራጀንና","እሚያሳየንማ","በሚዜነቱ","የወሰደላት","ሳያመነቱም","በፍልቅልቅነታቸው","የመንገደኞችም","ሽቶዎቻቸውን","አጠባዋን","እየጨነቃቸው"],"batch_number":195,"batch_label":"Words 5821-5850 (Batch 195/667)","model_version":null},{"id":"25a65fb5-40c9-45c2-b319-9bec8c74b258","created_at":"2026-03-04T19:57:02.556269+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_11.txt","batch_index":5730,"words":[{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማልቀስ","word":"በሚያለቅሰው","synonyms":["crying","weeping","lamenting","as he cries"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"መንበር","word":"በመንበሯ","synonyms":["on her seat","on her throne"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ጽላት","word":"የጽላቱን","synonyms":["of the tablet","of the ark","the tablet's"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"በረሮ","word":"ለበረሮና","synonyms":["for cockroaches","and for cockroaches"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"መሠረተ ልማት","word":"መሠረተልማቱን","synonyms":["the infrastructure","its infrastructure"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ኬንያ","word":"ስለኬንያው","synonyms":["about Kenya","concerning Kenya"],"importance":5},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መንዘር","word":"መንዝረው","synonyms":["having converted","having changed"